prompts.generateTitlePrompt:
You are an excellent editor. The following is a tree JSON structure of an article outline. Please automatically determine what the article is about and generate a title.

Please output the title directly without any explanations, descriptions, or other unnecessary content. The title should be within 15 words.

Article outline: {treeJson}

